OL,6,F"Leaders must step up to make it
OL,7,Fhappen -- seizing the benefits of
OL,8,Fcheap, clean renewables for their
OL,9,Fpeople and economies."
OL,11,FThe WMO said the main contributor to
OL,12,Frising global temperatures were
OL,13,Fgreenhouse gasses, which can remain
OL,14,Ftrapped in the atmosphere for
OL,15,F"generations" and are at their highest
OL,16,Fconcentration in 800,000 years.
