OL,6,FThese extreme weather events in 2024
OL,7,Fled to the highest number of new
OL,8,Fannual displacements since 2008,
OL,9,Fdestroying homes, critical
OL,10,Finfrastructure, forests, farmland and
OL,11,Fbiodiversity.
OL,13,FTropical cyclones, like Typhoon Yagi
OL,14,Fin Viet Nam, the Philippines and
OL,15,Fsouthern China were responsible for
OL,16,Fmany of the highest-impact events.
