OL,6,FAddressing what more could be done,
OL,7,FCeleste Saulo said they were,
OL,8,F"intensifying efforts to strengthen
OL,9,Fearly warning systems and climate
OL,10,Fservices to help decision-makers and
OL,11,Fsociety at large be more resilient to
OL,12,Fextreme weather and climate".
OL,14,F"We are making progress but need to go
OL,15,Ffurther and need to go faster," Ms
OL,16,FSaulo added. "Only half of all
OL,17,Fcountries worldwide have adequate
OL,18,Fearly warning systems. This must
OL,19,Fchange."
